1
00:00:01,067 --> 00:00:03,067
我叫Oliver Queen
My name is Oliver Queen.

2
00:00:04,067 --> 00:00:06,900
经历岛上地狱般的五年后
After five years on a hellish island,

3
00:00:06,900 --> 00:00:09,434
我回来了 心怀一个目标...
I have come home with only one goal...

4
00:00:09,434 --> 00:00:11,867
拯救这座城市
To save my city.

5
00:00:11,867 --> 00:00:16,900
但为此我不能再像以前一样杀戮
But to do so, I can't be the killer I once was.

6
00:00:16,900 --> 00:00:19,034
为了祭奠我的好友
To honor my friend's memory,

7
00:00:19,034 --> 00:00:22,000
我必须重塑自己
I must be someone else.

8
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:26,700
我必须伪装自身
I must be something else.

9
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:28,334
"绿箭侠" 前情提要...
Previously on "Arrow"...

10
00:00:28,334 --> 00:00:29,700
他已经没有利用价值了
This one's no longer of use to us.

11
00:00:29,700 --> 00:00:31,501
等等 他还有利用价值
Wait. He could still be useful.

12
00:00:31,501 --> 00:00:33,934
没错 一旦除掉他的那几个朋友
She's right. Once we get rid of his friends,

13
00:00:33,934 --> 00:00:36,100
我们需要他带领我们去墓地
we'll need him to lead us to the grave.

14
00:00:36,100 --> 00:00:37,634
你要回炼狱岛
You're going back to the island.

15
00:00:37,634 --> 00:00:39,634
你已经失去了父亲
Look, you already lost your dad.

16
00:00:39,634 --> 00:00:42,367
但是你母亲还在 她一定很想见你 
Your mom, she's still here. And I'm sure she'd love to see you.

17
00:00:42,367 --> 00:00:44,234
我不会去监狱看她
I'm not going to that prison.

18
00:00:44,234 --> 00:00:46,301
这是唯一能够报复她的方式
It's the only way I know how to hurt her.

19
00:00:46,301 --> 00:00:49,100
我真的很想恨你
And I want to hate you.

20
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:51,401
但是我做不到
But I can't.

21
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:54,833
我们之间没什么秘密可言
I didn't think that there were secrets kept between us.

22
00:00:54,833 --> 00:00:57,733
妈妈... 你到底在隐瞒什么?
Mom... what are you hiding now?

23
00:00:59,833 --> 00:01:02,967
我叫Moira Dearden Queen
My name is Moira Dearden Queen.

24
00:01:02,967 --> 00:01:06,800
我是Queen氏实业的执行总裁
I am the acting CEO of Queen Consolidated.

25
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:10,267
愿上帝原谅 我辜负了这座城市
And, God forgive me, I have failed this city.

26
00:01:10,267 --> 00:01:13,467
我被迫参与
I have been complicit in an undertaking

27
00:01:13,467 --> 00:01:16,034
一项极其恐怖的阴谋...
with one horrible purpose...

28
00:01:18,634 --> 00:01:22,467
摧毁贫民区的一切
to destroy the Glades and everyone in it.

29
00:01:22,467 --> 00:01:24,534
如果你住在贫民区
If you reside in the glades,

30
00:01:24,534 --> 00:01:27,167
请马上离开那里
please, you need to get out now.

31
00:01:27,167 --> 00:01:30,334
你们和你们的孩子正命悬一线
Your lives and the lives of your children depend on it.

32
00:01:30,334 --> 00:01:32,568
请离开那里
Please.

33
00:01:32,568 --> 00:01:36,201
狱长要我们马上撤离
Warden says we got to evacuate.

34
00:01:36,201 --> 00:01:38,601
帮忙把这些运走
Help me get these out of here.

35
00:01:38,601 --> 00:01:41,434
- 那些犯人呢?  - 让他们自生自灭
- What about the inmates?  - Leave 'em.

